ception":false,"start_time":"2026-03-26T16:44:36.929341+00:00","status":"completed"},"tags":[]},"source":["``` Now we have coefficient, we will try to find the intercept```"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"c9ec6d94","metadata":{"papermill":{"duration":0.005335,"end_time":"2026-03-26T16:44:36.946861+00:00","exception":false,"start_time":"2026-03-26T16:44:36.941526+00:00","status":"completed"},"tags":[]},"source":["\\begin{equation}\n","y = \\beta_0 + \\beta_1 x_1 + \\beta_2 x_2 + \\cdots + \\beta_n x_n\n","\\end{equation}"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"b910e39d","metadata":{"papermill":{"duration":0.005435,"end_time":"2026-03-26T16:44:36.957638+00:00","exception":false,"start_time":"2026-03-26T16:44:36.952203+00:00","status":"completed"},"tags":[]},"source":["# Finding the intercpt when betas given"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"9772b75f","metadata":{"papermill":{"duration":0.005447,"end_time":"2026-03-26T16:44:36.968432+00:00","exception":false,"start_time":"2026-03-26T16:44:36.962985+00:00","status":"completed"},"tags":[]},"source":["\n","\n","\\\n","\\begin{align*}\n","\\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial \\text{intercept}} \n","&= \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial \\text{intercept}} \\left( \\frac{1}{m} \\sum_{i=1}^m (y_i - \\hat{y}_i)^2 \\right) \\\\\n","&= \\frac{1}{m} \\sum_{i=1}^m 2 (y_i - \\hat{y}_i) \\frac{\\partial (y_i - \\hat{y}_i)}{\\partial \\text{intercept}} \\\\\n","&= \\frac{1}{m} \\sum_{i=1}^m 2 (y_i - \\hat{y}_i) \\cdot (-1) \\\\\n","&= -\\frac{2}{m} \\sum_{i=1}^m (y_i - \\hat{y}_i)\n","\\end{align*}\n","\\\n","\n","\n","\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":10,"id":"d84386a8","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.execute_input":"2026-03-26T16:44:36.980949Z","iopub.status.busy":"2026-03-26T16:44:36.980575Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-03-26T16:44:36.988582Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-03-26T16:44:36.987365Z"},"papermill":{"duration":0.016834,"end_time":"2026-03-26T16:44:36.990659+00:00","exception":false,"start_time":"2026-03-26T16:44:36.973825+00:00","status":"completed"},"tags":[]},"outputs":[],"source":["class GD:\n","    def __init__(self, x1,x2,x3,x4, lr=0.01):\n","        self.x1=x1\n","        self.x2=x2\n","        self.x3=x3\n","        self.x4=x4\n","        self.lr=lr\n","        self.intercept = 0\n","\n","\n","    def fit(self, X_train, y_train, epoch=1000):\n","        m=len(X_train)\n","        intercept=np.random.uniform(-1000,1000)\n","        \n","        for i in range(epoch):\n","            y_pred= self.intercept + self.x1*X_train.iloc[:,0] + self.x2*X_train.iloc[:,1] + self.x3*X_train.iloc[:,2] + self.x4*X_train.iloc[:,3]\n","\n","            grad=-(2/m)*np.sum(y_train-y_pred)\n","            \n","            self.intercept=self.intercept -self.lr*grad\n","            \n","        return self.intercept"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":11,"id":"8ca9f9d5","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.execute_input":"2026-03-26T16:44:37.004241Z","iopub.status.busy":"2026-03-26T16:44:37.003839Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-03-26T16:44:38.01727Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-03-26T16:44:38.016209Z"},"papermill":{"duration":1.02299,"end_time":"2026-03-26T16:44:38.019657+00:00","exception":false,"start_time":"2026-03-26T16:44:36.996667+00:00","status":"completed"},"tags":[]},"outputs":[{"data":{"text/plain":["np.float64(-33.60206754733134)"]},"execution_count":11,"metadata":{},"output_type":"execute_result"}],"source":["x1=2.85289351 \n","x2=1.01703572 \n","x3=0.47331832 \n","x4=0.19172629\n","gd=GD(x1,x2,x3,x4)\n","gd.fit(X_train, y_train)\n","#incpt"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"5436bb3e","metadata":{"papermill":{"duration":0.005354,"end_time":"2026-03-26T16:44:38.030458+00:00","exception":false,"start_time":"2026-03-26T16:44:38.025104+00:00","status":"completed"},"tags":[]},"source":["``` We get the same intercept as earlier which is -33.60206```"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"b5b6095b","metadata":{"papermill":{"duration":0.00551,"end_time":"2026-03-26T16:44:38.042404+00:00","exception":false,"start_time